---
// aabout.astro
import "./aabout.css";
---

<main class="about-section">
  <div class="about-container">

    <!-- Section 1 -->
    <section class="about-row">
      <div class="about-text">
        <h1 class="about-heading">A Studio That Works for Working Creators</h1>
        <p class="about-paragraph">
          Broken Duck Studio is a production space and membership community for YouTube creators. Located in Chiang Mai, it was built for people who want to make better content, stay consistent, and grow with purpose. This isn't a coworking space with a camera in the corner. It's a studio designed for actual production, quiet focus, and the kind of accountability that helps creators level up.
        </p>
        <p class="about-paragraph">
          Membership includes 24-hour access to the studio, use of production and meeting rooms, fast internet, lockers, guest passes, and access to our online scheduling system. You can see the full breakdown on the <a href="/membership">membership</a> page.
        </p>
      </div>
      <img src="/assets/images/Team1.svg" alt="Team illustration 1" class="about-image" />
    </section>

    <!-- Section 2 -->
    <section class="about-row reverse">
      <img src="/assets/images/Team2.svg" alt="Team illustration 2" class="about-image" />
      <div class="about-text">
        <h2 class="about-heading">What's Included</h2>
        <p class="about-paragraph">
          Members have access to two video studios, two voiceover booths, a shared office space, a bookable meeting room, and indoor and outdoor event areas. Studio time is scheduled through our fair-use booking system. See the full list on the <a href="/facility">facility</a> page.
        </p>
        <p class="about-paragraph">
          Every Sunday morning, we host <a href="/workshop">workshops</a> covering production techniques, editing workflows, channel strategy, monetization, and more. On the last Sunday of each month, we host a free <a href="/events">networking event</a> open to creators across Chiang Mai.
        </p>
        <p class="about-paragraph">
          For more flexibility, you can upgrade to one of our <a href="/packages">packages</a>. If you need additional cameras, lighting, or space, check out our <a href="/rental">rental</a> options, offered in partnership with Green Light Studio.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 3 -->
    <section class="about-row">
      <div class="about-text">
        <h2 class="about-heading">Coming Soon</h2>
        <p class="about-paragraph">
          We're preparing to launch a support track for creators who want to go beyond production. If you're growing a channel and looking for help with monetization, partnerships, or scaling, visit the <a href="/partner">partner</a> page to learn more about our upcoming MCN services.
        </p>
        <p class="about-paragraph">
          Everything we offer is designed to help creators get better at what they do. Whether you're starting from scratch or pushing toward full-time, Broken Duck Studio gives you the space, structure, and tools to move forward.
        </p>
      </div>
      <img src="/assets/images/Team2.svg" alt="Team illustration 2" class="about-image" />
    </section>

    <!-- Final Image Section -->
    <section class="about-image-full">
      <img src="/assets/images/Team3.svg" alt="Chiang Mai full-width illustration" />
    </section>
  </div>
</main>
